        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;SALT Marriage Penalty Elimination Act &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill increases from $10,000 to $20,000 the maximum amount of the tax deduction for state and local taxes for married couples whose adjusted gross income is less than $500,000 in 2023, thus eliminating the tax effect known as the marriage penalty.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
